short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Enhance your prompts. Let's your prompts everywhere.
short.zh_CN: 增强你的提示词系统。让你的提示词无处不在。

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The simplest, most reliable prompt assistant for ChatGPT

🚀 Features
  ⭐️ Quick access to pre-saved prompts
  ⭐️ Instantly insert prompts into ChatGPT's input box
  ⭐️ Customizable prompt library
  ⭐️ Effortless prompt management

🚀 How It Works
  ⭐️ Visit chatgpt.com
  ⭐️ Type "/" in the input box to activate the prompt list
  ⭐️ Select a prompt from the list to insert it into the input box
  ⭐️ Customize your prompt library in the extension settings

🚀 Permission Explanation
  ⭐️ "Read and change all your data on websites you visit": This permission is required to inject the prompt list and insert selected prompts into the ChatGPT input box on chatgpt.com.

Completely free, no ads
